      "score": 1577,
      "comments": 1102,
      "author": "mfiguiere",
      "published": "2026-07-21T20:09:52Z",
      "bullets": [
        "OpenAI and Hugging Face patched a security vulnerability exploited during automated model evaluation pipelines across shared ML infrastructure.",
        "Automated AI evaluation environments require strict sandbox isolation and restricted egress to prevent arbitrary code execution and credential theft.",
        "Engineering teams must audit Hugging Face Hub integrations and enforce zero-trust security controls on dynamic model evaluation workflows."
      ]
    },
